OL,3,CQuestions raised over conspiracy law
OL,4,Cafter GBH conviction of man overturned
OL,6,FQuestions are being raised about the
OL,7,Fpolice use of joint enterprise and
OL,8,Fconspiracy laws after the conviction
OL,9,Fof a young man from Greater Manchester
OL,10,Ffor causing grievous bodily harm was
OL,11,Foverturned.
OL,13,FAde Adedeji had no previous
OL,14,Fconvictions, he was going to study law
OL,15,Fat university and had written a book
OL,16,Fabout empowering his local community.
OL,18,FBut he was given an 8 year sentence
OL,19,Fdue to chat messages on the social
OL,20,Fmedia platform, Telegram, and he was
OL,21,Falso wrongly identified in a video.
