OL,3,CQuestions raised over conspiracy law
OL,4,Cafter GBH conviction of man overturned
OL,6,FIn court the prosecution argued that
OL,7,Fit was proof he was part of a gang,
OL,8,Fbut three Appeal Court judges have
OL,9,Fruled his conviction was unsafe, and
OL,10,Fhe's been freed after serving 3 years
OL,11,Fin jail.
OL,13,FAt the trial the court heard that
OL,14,Fafter Ade's best friend John Soyoye
OL,15,Fwas murdered in Moston in 2020 revenge
OL,16,Fattacks were discussed in postings on
OL,17,FTelegram, and Ade sent messages
OL,18,Fincluding the postcode of someone he
OL,19,Fbelieved was responsible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
