OL,6,FSpeaking from prison he said he
OL,7,Fregretted what he said in the chat,
OL,8,Fadding that John wouldn't have wanted
OL,9,Fanyone to take revenge.
OL,11,FBut the prosecution argued Ade was
OL,12,Fpart of the M40 gang, they used
OL,13,Fcomments from the group chat, a
OL,14,Fpicture of him with money to his ear
OL,15,Fand a 9 second video of a teenager
OL,16,Frapping in a blue bandana with gang
OL,17,Fcolours as proof of gang membership.
OL,19,FAde consistently denied that it was
OL,20,Fhim in the video, and said that it was
OL,21,Fa boy called Tyrone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
