OL,3,CQuestions raised over conspiracy law
OL,4,Cafter GBH conviction of man overturned
OL,6,FLast December Tyrone Numa came forward
OL,7,Ffor an appeal hearing and gave
OL,8,Fevidence to confirm it was him in the
OL,9,Fvideo.
OL,11,FHis evidence led to the quashing of
OL,12,FAde's conviction.
OL,14,FThe court said "The video clip was
OL,15,Frelied on to show that Ade was closer
OL,16,Fto the M40 gang than he accepted and
OL,17,Fwas part of the chain of evidence
OL,18,Flinking Ade to the gang."
