OL,6,FNow legal experts are raising concerns
OL,7,Fthat the laws used to convict Ade are
OL,8,Funreliable.
OL,10,FDr Patrick Williams explains, "Where
OL,11,Fan individual may have committed and
OL,12,Foffence, joint enterprise allows for
OL,13,Fall individuals to be potentially
OL,14,Fconvicted".
OL,16,FKeir Monteith KC says "Conspiracy is a
OL,17,Flittle bit different, people,
OL,18,Fcertainly within my profession would
OL,19,Fsee it as easier to prove than joint
OL,20,Fenterprise."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
