OL,6,F"This explored all GMP homicide
OL,7,Finvestigations dating back to 2015, of
OL,8,Fwhich 5.8% were joint enterprise cases.
OL,10,F"It found no evidence that any
OL,11,Fstereotyping, or particularly a "Gang
OL,12,FMatrix", is used to influence decision
OL,13,Fmaking on investigations. The report
OL,14,Falso found that black people are
OL,15,Fdisproportionately more likely to be
OL,16,Fan offender or a victim. Sadly,
OL,17,Fvictims of homicide are twice as
OL,18,Flikely to be black."
